eager scener like Curt Cool as captain
of this 37th issue (at least) of the
EC. Magical Moments is back for the
second time in 1999, or should I say
3rd ? Maybe you have noticed that a
slightly changed 'MM' corner ended up
in Retro 4 while it was published
earlier in the Eurochart 36. The
reason for this was quite simple
really, Retro died back then. (Or so I
thought..)

»CL0:Soda was no where to be found, the 4th
issue should have been out for weeks
so I left the mag and allianced with
the EC. Then suddenly Soda came back
and released Retro 4. Afterwards we
tried to make a 5th issue but then
Darkus left for his own magazine (soon
to be released) Soda joined Scenetime
as Main-ed (read about this later on
