»CL9:Magical Moments History
»CL7:--------------------------------------
"Every Generation has a legend; Every
saga has a beginning" This also counts
for my corner. Magical Moments (from
now on MM) originates from 1995. In
the middle of this year I made the
concept and was advertised in Trinity
issue 1 (which by the way was
main-edited by me and Sane :) However
this magazine project went up in
smoke. Thus I contacted a new main-ed
in the scene called Fishwave, who
gladly refused my corner and
Rokdazone's Marvellous Lunatics Ball
for issue 2, since he didn't want to
have such dominating parts by other
writers in his magazine (Hmm do I
remember this correctly Adrian?)
Luckily Buzz issue 7 (At The Party
1995) was willing to publish my first
MM corner.. Later on when I
coordinated nAh's new Musicdisk, I
decided to call it 'Moments' :)
Ironicly pointing out that (scene)
life has just a few moments which will
be very special.. At the end of 1998 I
decided to continue the MM corner, and
now the 3rd edition (of nine) is
finished. Hastalavista baby.. :)




